                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>15<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> Augt./59</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Pha</p>\n            <p>Rev. DrSir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your esteemed Letter<lb/> I duly received and communicated<lb/> its\n                contents—in as far as they<lb/> concern him—to <persName>Mr Benjamin</persName><lb/>\n                who intends to write to you<lb/> direct.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">In consequence of your<lb/> remarks, I got the Israelite<lb/> and\n                read the article in<lb/> question. It is, as usual a<lb/> gross fraud, &amp; an\n                impudent<lb/> speculation on the ignorance<lb/> of the public. I hold the<lb/> man\n                &amp; his paper in too<lb/> great contempt to be<lb/> moved by any thing he</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3736mn5v/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
